<i>noun</i>: 횡단로 [횡단노/휑단노], 첩경 [첩꼉], 지름길 [지름낄] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>횡단로 [횡단노/휑단노]</dt><br>
<dd>1. crosscut road; shortcut</dd><br>
<dd>길이나 도로 등을 건너질러 가는 길.</dd><br>
<dd>A route that cuts through a road or street.</dd><br>
<dd>2. route for crossing; transverse route</dd><br>
<dd>대륙이나 바다 등을 가로 방향으로 지나거나 건너서 가는 길.</dd><br>
<dd>A route that passes or cuts through a continent or an ocean horizontally in a direction from east to west.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>첩경 [첩꼉]</dt><br>
<dd>1. shortcut</dd><br>
<dd>목적지까지 빠르게 갈 수 있는 길.</dd><br>
<dd>A shorter way to get to a destination.</dd><br>
<dd>2. shortcut</dd><br>
<dd>(비유적으로) 쉽고 빠른 방법.</dd><br>
<dd>(figurative) A method that reduces the time or energy needed to accomplish something.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>지름길 [지름낄]</dt><br>
<dd>1. shortcut</dd><br>
<dd>목적지까지 빠르게 갈 수 있는 길.</dd><br>
<dd>A shorter way to get to a destination.</dd><br>
<dd>2. shortcut</dd><br>
<dd>(비유적으로) 쉽고 빠른 방법.</dd><br>
<dd>(figurative) A method that reduces the time or energy needed to accomplish something.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>